LeetCode 3 — Plus One

plus_one.py

class Solution:

    def plusOne(self, digits):

        number = int("".join(map(str, digits)))

        number += 1

        return list(map(int, str(number)))


obj = Solution()

print(obj.plusOne([1,2,3]))

Output:

[1, 2, 4]


